INSERT [dbo].[Contents] ([Id], [Value], [ParentId], [ParentType], [CreatedOn]) VALUES (3, N'<b>If you are not taking clopidogrel (Plavix®)</b> right now, you do not need to do anything.  In the future, if you need clopidogrel (Plavix®) you should tell your doctor that you are a poor metabolizer based on a genetic test.<br/>
<br/>
<b>If you are taking clopidogrel (Plavix®)</b>, you should discuss with your doctor your test result.<br/>
Your doctor may:
<ul>
<li>Do other tests to see how you are  responding to clopidogrel</li>
<li>Give you another medication that is not clopidogrel to treat your condition</li>
<li>Discuss your treatment with another physician or specialist</li>
